<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5399762>
    dc:description "FIG. 10. — Sclerotized structures of Euryhaliotrema n. gen. species; A-G, Euryhaliotrema bychowskyi (Obodnikova, 1976) n. comb.; A, ventral anchor; B, vagina (ventral view); C, hook; D, copulatory complex (ventral view); E, dorsal anchor; F, ventral bar; G, dorsal bar; H-N, Euryhaliotrema paralonchuri (Lugue & Iannacone, 1989) n. comb; H, vagina (ventral view); I, hook; J, ventral bar; K, copulatory complex (ventral view); L, dorsal anchor; M, dorsal bar; N, ventral anchor. Scale bar: 25 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5399762/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

